WEBVTT

00:08.273 --> 00:09.776
Hey, Antonio.

00:09.808 --> 00:11.244
Hey!

00:11.276 --> 00:13.112
- Hey.
- Hey.

00:13.145 --> 00:14.346
Sorry.

00:14.379 --> 00:16.148
Are you okay?

00:16.181 --> 00:17.317
Yeah, yeah.

00:17.373 --> 00:18.978
- I'm good, I'm good.
- Good.

00:19.003 --> 00:20.753
- You good?
- Good, yeah, all good.

00:20.787 --> 00:22.721
- Yeah.
- Are you going in?

00:22.755 --> 00:24.924
Good, me too.

00:24.956 --> 00:26.926
- Should we walk?
- Yeah.

00:26.959 --> 00:28.195
Okay.

00:30.059 --> 00:32.261
Well I for one am very glad
that we can be together

00:32.293 --> 00:33.931
and it's not awkward.

00:35.431 --> 00:36.899
Are you here for Platt's thing?

00:36.932 --> 00:38.144
'Cause I've never seen Mouch so excited

00:38.168 --> 00:39.536
about anything in his whole life.

00:39.568 --> 00:41.572
He made a cinnamon roll casserole
for the occasion.

00:41.605 --> 00:43.239
What the hell's that?

00:43.273 --> 00:45.876
What's the big deal, man?
Just do me this favor.

00:45.909 --> 00:48.579
I'm not live tweeting
a threeminute conversation.

00:48.611 --> 00:50.913
It's a threeminute conversation.

00:50.946 --> 00:52.983
Local access, Mouch, I mean...

00:53.016 --> 00:54.493
Who do you propose
is going to be tuning in

00:54.517 --> 00:55.551
for these live tweets?

00:55.584 --> 00:57.119
What are you doing here?

00:57.153 --> 00:58.898
I thought PD was having
their own viewing party.

00:58.922 --> 01:00.190
She's on in 30 minutes.

01:00.223 --> 01:01.992
As much as I love Trudy.
I'm here for Eva.

01:02.025 --> 01:04.060
- You guys seen her?
- She's down there with Gabby.

01:04.093 --> 01:07.063
Third door on the left.

01:07.096 --> 01:08.197
There you go, Rapunzel.

01:08.230 --> 01:09.498
Get your stuff. We're going.

01:09.532 --> 01:11.000
What? Why?

01:11.033 --> 01:12.211
You said I could hang
with Aunt Gabby all day.

01:12.235 --> 01:13.604
Yeah, she can. She's fine.

01:13.637 --> 01:15.205
You're not staying. You're grounded.

01:15.238 --> 01:16.873
No more phone. No social media.

01:16.907 --> 01:19.310
- Let's go.
- What? What did I do?

01:24.480 --> 01:26.182
All right, that's not
what it looks like.

01:26.215 --> 01:27.950
- I can explain.
- Is that not your profile?

01:27.983 --> 01:29.920
- No, it is, but it's not...
- Under a fake name

01:29.952 --> 01:31.520
- so I can't monitor it.
- No.

01:31.554 --> 01:33.123
It's just a second account.

01:33.155 --> 01:34.533
It's the one I use at my friends...

01:34.557 --> 01:36.626
It's the account where
you posted a dozen pictures

01:36.660 --> 01:38.595
of yourself partying and drinking.

01:38.628 --> 01:41.164
I did not post any of those.

01:41.197 --> 01:44.034
- Last weekend... Hey!
- That was...

01:44.066 --> 01:45.669
Last weekend when you told me

01:45.702 --> 01:49.072
you were studying late at Taryn's house.

01:49.104 --> 01:51.974
- Did you not tell me that?
- I...

01:52.007 --> 01:54.010
Go get your stuff.

01:54.643 --> 01:57.113
Don't look at her. Go.

01:58.148 --> 02:00.517
Eva, give me your phone.

02:04.086 --> 02:06.122
You know you look just like Dad, right?

02:06.155 --> 02:08.190
You even got that
forehead vein thing going.

02:08.223 --> 02:09.459
That's papa.

02:11.427 --> 02:13.029
Come on. Let's go.

02:14.431 --> 02:16.132
Later, Eva.

02:16.165 --> 02:18.534
Every single person
I know has two profiles.

02:18.568 --> 02:20.003
It's just for privacy.

02:20.035 --> 02:21.538
That's not privacy. That's hiding.

02:21.570 --> 02:23.648
You're making those photos
into something they're not.

02:23.672 --> 02:25.207
You can't trust the Internet, Dad.

02:25.241 --> 02:26.944
It always looks worse than it is.

02:26.976 --> 02:29.313
If you would just
let me explain it to you

02:29.345 --> 02:31.682
instead of you seizing
my phone without cause.

02:31.714 --> 02:33.983
Platt's on in two. Everyone! Adam!

02:34.016 --> 02:35.618
- Antonio, come on.
- We're not staying.

02:35.652 --> 02:37.028
I'm gonna do the paperwork at home.

02:37.052 --> 02:38.421
Hey, Eva. What's up, kid?

02:38.455 --> 02:39.989
My father's a fascist.

02:40.022 --> 02:42.358
Okay, I don't know what to do with that.

02:42.391 --> 02:44.360
Okay, everybody be quiet.

02:44.393 --> 02:45.361
Platt's on TV.

02:45.395 --> 02:47.130
Betty's sitting down to discuss

02:47.163 --> 02:48.432
the new friendly face

02:48.464 --> 02:49.533
of the Chicago PD

02:49.565 --> 02:51.033
with Sergeant Trudy Platt.

02:51.066 --> 02:52.143
- What friendly face is that?
- Betty.

02:52.167 --> 02:53.369
Thank you, Sheri.

02:53.403 --> 02:55.304
I'm so excited to be here today

02:55.338 --> 02:58.241
with Sergeant Trudy Platt
from the 21st District...

02:58.273 --> 03:00.242
She couldn't possibly
hate this any more.

03:00.276 --> 03:02.244
Thank you so much
for coming this morning.

03:02.278 --> 03:05.282
It's my pleasure.
I'm hap... I'm happy to be here.

03:05.314 --> 03:07.483
This is like Christmas.

03:07.516 --> 03:09.618
Those photos don't show
what you think they do.

03:09.652 --> 03:12.221
Okay, we did go to Taryn's
house, and then we got a call

03:12.255 --> 03:14.291
- from Becca that she needed...
- Eva, stop!

03:14.324 --> 03:15.667
You put your whole life on that thing.

03:15.691 --> 03:17.027
I don't need you to explain.

03:17.059 --> 03:18.270
I can see exactly what you're doing

03:18.294 --> 03:20.330
and who you are. And you know what?

03:20.362 --> 03:22.199
I don't like
who you've become very much.

03:22.231 --> 03:24.266
In the neighborhoods that they serve.

03:24.300 --> 03:26.403
Combating crime problems together

03:26.435 --> 03:28.571
along with...

03:28.605 --> 03:31.340
- Is everything okay?
- I think that's coming

03:31.374 --> 03:34.344
- from my office.
- What was that?

03:36.000 --> 03:42.074
Advertise your product or brand here
